fields.fieldText: Do you need your PO Box mail or office mail picked up or delivered?
fields.helpText:
Choose yes if the customer needs a Stand Alone Mail Collection, charges will apply for this service.
This is separate to an eParcel collection.

fields.name: Do_you_send_Addressed_or_unaddressed_mail
fields.fieldText: Do you send addressed or unaddressed mail?
fields.helpText:
Addressed mail is all letters with both name and address of recipient on the article.
Unaddressed mail does not have the name or address of any recipient on the articles. These articles will be delivered to postcode areas the customer has chosen when using the service.

fields.name: Do_you_require_a_payment_facility_to_accept_payments_for_goods_and_services

fields.name: Are_you_a_charity_or_local_council_wanting_to_send_letters_or_publications

Local Councils may be eligible for special services for letters and publications.
